Hello,

This repository holds several system administration scripts that are
useful for me in some way. 
 Feel free to explore, copy, fork or whatever you want to do with them.

INDEX
-----

bash/firewall/ipv4-linux.sh -------- Firewall Script for iptables with blacklists.
bash/firewall/ipv4-routeros.sh ----- Firewall Script for RouterOs with blacklists.
python/mail/extract.py ------------- Mail Binary extractor for security purposes.
python/tx/tx.py -------------------- Script to automate transfer of files.
python/vsftp/vsftp-file-sync ------- Script to keep synced an vsftp folder with another
js/rutorrent/rutorrent.user.js ----- Greasemonkey userscript that sends links to a seedbox
